        <span data-i18n-en>Level up everything you can on your server!</span>
    </p>
    <p class="mb-10 text-center opacity-60 text-sm" style="font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;">
        <span data-i18n-pt>Necessário ser um Host de Path of Titans.</span>
        <span data-i18n-en>Requires being a Path of Titans server host.</span>
    </p>

